-- ECB Should Weigh Bundesbank’s Concern, Asmussen Tells Maerkische
-- B y   A n n e t t e   W e i s b a c h
-- 2012-08-31T18:12:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-31/ecb-should-weigh-bundesbank-s-concern-asmussen-tells-maerkische.html
 European Central Bank Executive
Board Member Joerg Asmussen said that there are good reasons why
the ECB is modeled after the Bundesbank and he attaches
importance to the Bundesbank’s views,  Maerkische Allgemeine 
reported.  “If the Bundesbank has concerns, I have to take that
seriously,” Asmussen said in an interview with the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Annette Weisbach in Frankfurt at 
